roomai.kuhn.KuhnPokerAction module¶

class roomai.kuhn.KuhnPokerAction.KuhnPokerAction(key)[source]¶

Bases: roomai.common.common.AbstractAction

The KuhnPoker action used by the normal players. There are only two actions: bet and check. Examples of usages:

>> import roomai.kuhn

>> action = roomai.kuhn.KuhnPokerAction.lookup(“bet”)

>> action.key

“bet”

>> action = roomai.kuhn.KuhnPokerAction.lookup(“check”)

>> action.key

“check”

key¶

The key of the KuhnPoker action, “bet” or “check”.

roomai.kuhn.KuhnPokerChanceAction module¶

class roomai.kuhn.KuhnPokerChanceAction.KuhnPokerChanceAction(key)[source]¶

Bases: roomai.common.common.AbstractAction

The KuhnPoker action used by the chance player. Example of usages:

>> import roomai.kuhn

>> action = roomai.kuhn.KuhnPokerChanceAction(“0,1”)

>> action.key

“0,1”

>> action.number_for_player0

0

>> action.number_for_player1

1

key¶

The key of the KuhnPokerChance action, for example, “0,1”
